initial_predicted_sql: SELECT programmes.title, SUM(projects.ec_max_contribution) FROM programmes JOIN project_programmes ON programmes.code = project_programmes.programme JOIN projects ON projects.unics_id = project_programmes.project GROUP BY programmes.title
final_predicted_sql: SELECT programmes.title, SUM(projects.ec_max_contribution) FROM programmes JOIN project_programmes ON programmes.code = project_programmes.programme JOIN projects ON projects.unics_id = project_programmes.project GROUP BY programmes.title
